nnada/2019/feb/09/chuttu-chuttu-girl-ashika-ranganath-on-board-for-sharan-starrer-avatar-purusha-1936464.html|title=Chuttu Chuttu girl Ashika Ranganath on board for Sharan-starrer 'Avatar Purusha'|website=The New Indian Express|access-date=2019-12-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/kannada/movies/news/ashika-ranganaths-look-from-avatara-purusha-revealed/articleshow/70529675.cms|title=Ashika Ranganath's look from Avatara Purusha revealed - Times of India|website=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2019-12-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/kannada/nri-return-ashika-ranganath-goes-ethnic-in-avatara-purusha/articleshow/70585061.cms|title=NRI-return Ashika Ranganath goes ethnic in Avatara Purusha - Times of India|website=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2019-12-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/sandalwood/131119/big-budget-films-in-her-kitty.html|title=Big-budget films in her kitty|last=SM|first=Shashiprasad|date=2019-11-13|website=Deccan Chronicle|language=en|access-date=2019-12-17}}</ref>\n|-\n|9\n| style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\" |''Raymo'' {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n|Mohana\n|[[Pavan Wadeyar]]\n|''Filming<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/kannada/movies/news/ashika-ranganath-to-star-opposite-ishan-in-pavan-wadeyars-next/articleshow/69741708.cms|title=Ashika Ranganath to star opposite Ishan in Pavan Wadeyar's next - Times of India|website=The Times of India|language=en|access-date=2019-12-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2019/jun/19/pavan-wadeyars-next-with-actor-ishan-is-titled-remo-12407.html|title=Pavan Wadeyar's next with actor Ishan is titled Raymo|website=The New Indian Express|access-date=2019-12-17}}</ref>''\n|-\n|10\n| style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\" |''Rangamandira''{{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been release